- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): The paper applies the proposed method to the problem of classification of hyperspectral satellite imagery, which falls under the domain of computer vision. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper introduces a new concept of transport operators on graphs, which can be seen as a new data structure for representing complex datasets. 
- cs.NA (Numerical Analysis): The paper presents fundamental properties of the transport operators and demonstrates their flexibility through diverse examples of transformations, which involves numerical analysis. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks): The concept of transport operators on graphs can be applied to various types of networks, including social and information networks.
